  "detailed_description": "Endless Furry Killer 3D is the second installment of the Furry Killer Series!<br>The game is currently in alpha development process.<br>DISCLAIMER:<br>ENDLESS FURRY KILLER 3D DOES NOT <br>CONDONE OR SUPPORT ANY TYPE OF<br>REAL WORLD VIOLENCE OR HATE TOWARD<br>ANY GROUP OF ANY KIND!<br><br>Key Features:<br>1. Six Weapons, pistol, shotgun, mini-gun, rail-gun, and flamer.<br>2. Endless Furry combat. Play till you die!<br>3. Four ready to play levels. Easy, medium, and hard modes, and one test level.<br>4. Systems that keeps track of players score and time alive.<br>5. Hidden Easter Eggs!<br>6. Consistent updates!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1519470/extras/8d55933d486b4c38b7f7562601a20e65.avif?t=1755742802\" width=450 height=175 /></span>",
